on_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-mysterines">神秘乐队</a>取消了即将到来的英国和欧盟巡演。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-mysterines-live-in-liverpool-radar-3197612">神秘人住在利物浦：家乡英雄的喧闹回归</a></strong></li></ul><p>这支利物浦垃圾摇滚四人乐队原定于 10 月 18 日在都柏林举办一系列秋季演出。然而，今天（8 月 31 日）他们宣布取消演出日期。</p><p>在分享给 Instagram 的一份声明中，乐队告诉歌迷，“由于最近的情况”，他们“心情沉重”地取消了所有计划的巡演日期。目前尚不清楚具体情况如何。</p><p> “我们非常高兴能与你们分享这次旅行，但经过仔细考虑，我们决定这不是我们目前最好的决定，”他们说。 “我们向所有期待看到我们表演的人致以诚挚的歉意，对于由此造成的失望，我们深表歉意。”</p><p> “请知道，您的支持对我们来说意味着整个世界，”他们继续说道。 “感谢您这段时间的理解和耐心。”</p><p>门票可在购买时退款。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_VyU0gNG_E/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: cent